reviewText:
I don't know what the guy who commented that there was no frontal nudity was watching but this was a typical Rusty Nail Production. Pretty girls and artistic nudity. My only complaint would be to much Sarah. It seems like in every compilation video there are at least 2 spots with her in it.
It is worth the money by far.

WHILE THE MOVIE IS WHAT IS PROMISED , IT'S BECOMES BORING AFTER THE THIRD OR FOURTH SCENE.  EACH SEGMENT IS THE SAME AIMLESS ACTING.  JUST SOME GIRL TAKING OFF HER CLOTHES.  FROM THE TITLE, YOU WOULD THINK THERE WOULD BE MORE NUDITY THAN THERE IS (FRONTAL NUDITY WAS SOMEWHAT RARE.) THE GIRLS ARE GOOD LOOKING BUT NOTHING EXCEPTIONAL.  WORTH A RENTAL NOT A PURCHASE. IT'S ALREADY ON MY BACK SHELF.
